#: ui/templates/platform/_hierarchy_help.html:21
msgid ""
"Strateji bir piramittir: üstte <b>ortak yön katmanları</b>, altta ise Alt"
" Strateji'den <b>iki kola ayrılan icra</b> vardır. Her katmanın amacı, "
"süresi ve sorumlusu farklıdır."
msgstr ""
"Strategy is a pyramid: at the top are the <b>shared direction layers</b>,"
" and at the bottom is the <b>execution that splits into two branches</b> "
"from the Sub-Strategy. Each layer has a different purpose, duration, and "
"owner."

